---The DoG of NoTTuB was here...</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ustormhaven.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stormhaven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>FAQ/Index Moderator</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/14/01 9:55:45 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://web2.airmail.net/naomi/amalgam/forum/stormhaven.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best weapons at 15th</span><hr size=1> Hmm... if I remember correctly, at level 15, &quot;massive damage&quot; was still around 20pts.  *If you care* about melee stats, this is the time to build them up.  Quite honestly, you should be ok with fine steel weapons unless you're fighting against magic-only creatures.<br>
<br>
1hb: Screaming Mace, Enam. Black Mace<br>
2hb: Observer Staff, Glowing Wooden Crook (was this 1h?  I forget)<br>
1hs: Obsidian Scimitar, Runed Falchon <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usomberlainwayfaerer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Somberlain Wayfaerer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/17/01 5:06:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best weapons at 15th</span><hr size=1> The Screaming Mace for 1hb and Glowing Wooden Crook for 2hb seem to be the weapons of choice at your level.  On both my druid and shaman, I spent a lot of time in the teens and low 20s with a 2hb, although I now use a Sharkbone Warhammer (1hb) or Obsidian Scimitar (1hs) with a shield.  For damage output, 2hb is great, but right now there aren't a lot of 2hb weapons in the game that make the skill worthwhile at the higher levels.  <br>
